{"tid":1290695,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 原來專業嘅香港警察係咁樣","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:42:19.000Z","uid":232671,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d97c3971c00b9fed4b682c17b393ab65dd184c","tid":1290695,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>Quote</strong><br />\n大家好，我係片中主角。等我用文字補充影片中缺少嘅情節。因入村尾班車爆人，我只好坐在村口落嘅17號紅Van，大約要行20分鐘到家，落車行完天橋，見鐵馬旁有架Ofo共享單車，便上前查看睇下用唔用到，注意共享單車旁邊沒有一架私人單車，剛好被巡邏警察看見我嘅行為，佢地上前截查我，夜晚加村口人少的環境，我覺得佢地係合理地截查我，但佢地冇問我點解係到，係唔係住附近，直接懷疑我偷單車，之後查我身分證，我都覺得合理，但之後要搜身，我便問片中聲大夾惡嘅警察以咩標準懷疑我偷單車以及做搜身的決定，他話係警察法例嘅權利，問完之後佢便開始以失控嘅態度處理我，沒有處理問題，之後就係以上影片。警民關係差，唔係冇原因。<br />\n<strong>Unquote</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002711881371/videos/1934268526673525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002711881371%2Fvideos%2F1934268526673525%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zfuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=fc81a484\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002711881371/videos/1934268526673525/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cde209b9bc2e8cd6bc64ea38e5ecdb00d096979","tid":1290695,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48f0e831daf8b35be8717204266b9501bfdae235","tid":1290695,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"old news wo ching"},{"pid":"2fdc3bb4efdf8dce96bf848fdfdd427a4f48ea0f","tid":1290695,"uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"-_-似維園阿叔多過警察"},{"pid":"5fd1953a2af7a88cfa6153b77aed9d8ecbed3f90","tid":1290695,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f0e831daf8b35be8717204266b9501bfdae235","tid":1290695,"uid":